Package: smd.and.more
Type: Package
Title: t-test with Graph of Standardized Mean Difference, and More
Version: 1.1-0
Date: 2010-04-23
Author: David W. Gerbing, Portland State University
Maintainer: David W. Gerbing <davidg@sba.pdx.edu>
Suggests: MBESS
Description: The function smd.t.test provides enhanced output for the
        independent groups t-test for the analysis of the mean
        difference. This output includes a variety of descriptive and
        inferential statistics, including the standardized mean
        difference or Cohen's d. The output includes an ODDSMD plot,
        which displays the Overlapping Density Distributions of the two
        groups as well as provides a visual display of the mean
        difference and Standardized Mean Difference. Other functions
        provide for the t-test from descriptive statistics, color
        plotting, a power curve with colors and a quick read of csv
        data.
